title: Seriously Riot, get your act together, Low ELO sucks balls

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: I don't even know what to say. At the end Lucian called us "Shit %%%%s" and throughout the whole game Trundle was complaining about us.

replies.body: if you were that good you wouldnt be in low elo.

Oh no, you don't get it, being in the solo queue this season is harder than a priest at mass.

I just finished another game, my stats were that much better than the rest of the map it is not funny and it still took 48 minutes to win with one player still being level 17 at the end, such is the difference in skill at this rank.
